  "3008270": {
    "name": "Tree of Sacrifice",
    "steam_appid": 3008270,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灾难降临后，有的地方鸟语花香，但是有的地方却变得满目疮痍，怪物横行，普通的植物再也无法正常生长，人们不得不通过挑选大龄冒险者进入此处获取必要的资源。据说，一切灾难的源头都来自一位魔王。如今你将独自前往岛屿中心位置的巨树寻找一切的根源和解决办法，却从此一去不回……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras/857894056a408d88e11c4a44ee0ac1bd.avif?t=1764271436\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras_big/857894056a408d88e11c4a44ee0ac1bd.avif?t=1764271436 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras/9e5268d8b25b5e20cf388954be2c163d.avif?t=1764271436\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras_big/9e5268d8b25b5e20cf388954be2c163d.avif?t=1764271436 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特色:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在巨树内部不断前进，慎重地选择物品搭配，探索战斗、商店、事件的前因后果；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >技能通过WERT按键即可释放，但释放的顺序尤为重要，玩家将需要合理的搭配技能与构建独特的物品属性，充分发挥其独特魅力；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras/101aead4a455a1c1a6e4c926edfc54af.avif?t=1764271436\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras_big/101aead4a455a1c1a6e4c926edfc54af.avif?t=1764271436 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏模式:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒险之旅：标准剧情模式，由战斗+剧情演绎组成，每个关卡将经历一个充满挑战的 boss 战，敌人被击败后玩家可以选择了解敌人的前世今生，已经存在于此的原因，开发者为此给每一个存在于此的敌人赋予了存在的意义；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras/3f2868273479e2d347a28a44b2f54a51.avif?t=1764271436\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras_big/3f2868273479e2d347a28a44b2f54a51.avif?t=1764271436 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras/0c1e95682c8d0f4ff3948009fa7d6df5.avif?t=1764271436\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras_big/0c1e95682c8d0f4ff3948009fa7d6df5.avif?t=1764271436 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >速通模式：根据每一关卡的敌人信息提前搭配合适的物品与之战斗,以最短的时间到达树冠,登记各项参数后在排行榜留下你的大名；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras/edca20bd8d6561c9fd668defb586c7e3.avif?t=1764271436\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras_big/edca20bd8d6561c9fd668defb586c7e3.avif?t=1764271436 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无尽战斗：在线1V1对战，用不断变化的物品属性通过强大的临场应对能力对战同样的敌人，你能坚持多久呢？[开发中...]</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在本作中除了体验到紧张刺激的回合制策略战斗外，最重要的是能够沉浸式感受到每个与你对战的个体所存在的意义，以及为什么存在于此，你为何存在于此！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1、在Demo版本中玩家体验到爬塔+回合制策略的战斗模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2、结束战斗根据玩家的选择可以提升战斗难度 / 维持难度的同时了解与你战斗的敌人为何存在，我们给每个敌人单独做了独特的小片段动画展示</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3、同时添加了排行榜，成就系统等内容[steam以及游戏内部均实现]</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4、提供了云端数据存储以及在线留言板形式的异步交流，玩家可以通过游戏功能模块在相同的空间中浏览到不同时间下其他玩家发起的交流</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5、玩家可以将战斗时的自身数据进行保存提交至云端后，其他玩家通过游戏内部模块下载后与之进行对战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[本作当前仅支持中文] - [部分字幕添加了英文]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作说明：</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗场景 - 道具栏 - 操作按键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras/c5aaa84cdbe3b93c7d75ba571b70550f.avif?t=1764271436\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras/084a01b92d5365507716b53cfe83cfe8.avif?t=1764271436\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras/0168732196237fc15ad768aa330e10b9.avif?t=1764271436\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras/650e488d723e068e7e8cb23797aef586.avif?t=1764271436\" width=64 height=64 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗场景 - 技能栏 - 操作按键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras/89d9868caf445b3a7169f626e58940b0.avif?t=1764271436\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras/9effc8e1cfa1c2d8b4a0f5be02d6d70b.avif?t=1764271436\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras/790e23a38f1b6acb076900aac5493fb3.avif?t=1764271436\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras/8c2bf21409cbe32a65163eabc6772e7b.avif?t=1764271436\" width=64 height=64 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗场景 - 战法栏 - 操作按键</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras/2de552f9e2cbd0c546e4584753456c96.avif?t=1764271436\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras/0c41d15bb8e2f4daa8d01d141a8efc1a.avif?t=1764271436\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras/4835d6a8c66391c7c07728fcd912861a.avif?t=1764271436\" width=64 height=64 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏场景快捷按键</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008270/extras/28c240643ae8cb245e162cecf7e11126.avif?t=1764271436\" width=96 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
